      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "6. Volunteer Training Materials and Onboarding Docs",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Churches constantly onboard new volunteers: greeters, kids' ministry workers, tech team members, small group facilitators. Writing training manuals and onboarding guides from scratch every time is exhausting.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Dry Ground AI can draft role-specific training documents, FAQ sheets, and onboarding checklists. You give it the role, the expectations, and any doctrinal specifics, and it produces a clean, organized document your team can actually use.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This use case surprised me. I hadn't thought of it initially, but when a church administrator mentioned she used it to create a 20-page kids' ministry volunteer handbook in one sitting, I realized how versatile this platform really is.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
