      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "VBS season. Fall kickoff. Marriage retreat. Missions week. Churches run events year-round, and each one needs flyers, emails, social posts, announcements, and follow-up messages.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Dry Ground AI lets you input an event description and instantly receive a full communication kit: email sequences, bulletin blurbs, social media copy, and even talking points for stage announcements. A communications pastor in Ohio told me his VBS promotion took 3 hours instead of 3 days this year.",
            "marks": []
