        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Dry Ground AI is an AI-powered content platform designed specifically for Christian ministries and religious organizations. It generates sermon outlines, daily devotionals, outreach emails, small group study guides, social media captions, and event communication materials. You provide the topic, scripture, or event details, and it drafts polished, theologically informed content in minutes.",
